---
import MainLayout from "@layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | ExpatDrive"
  description="ExpatDrive privacy policy. Your study data stays on your device."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: March 3, 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-primary leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy">Summary</h2>
      <p>
        ExpatDrive does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. All study progress is stored
        locally in your browser using localStorage. We don't use cookies for tracking, don't require
        accounts, and don't share data with third parties.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mt-8">What data is stored</h2>
      <p>
        ExpatDrive stores the following data locally in your browser:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Practice exam scores and history</li>
        <li>Spaced repetition card scheduling data</li>
        <li>Vocabulary drill progress</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This data never leaves your device. It is stored in your browser's localStorage and can be
        cleared at any time through the Progress page or by clearing your browser data.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mt-8">Analytics and tracking</h2>
      <p>
        We do not use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, or any third-party tracking tools.
        We may use privacy-respecting, cookie-free analytics in the future (such as Plausible or
        Fathom), which do not track individual users.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mt-8">Third-party services</h2>
      <p>
        ExpatDrive uses the following third-party services:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — to load the Inter typeface. Google may log font requests (IP address, user agent). See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-navy-light underline hover:text-navy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's privacy policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — for hosting. Vercel processes standard HTTP request data (IP address, user agent) as part of serving the website. See <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-navy-light underline hover:text-navy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vercel's privacy policy</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mt-8">Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        ExpatDrive does not knowingly collect data from children under 13. The service is intended for
        adults preparing for driver's license exams.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mt-8">Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        If we make material changes to this privacy policy, we will update the "Last updated" date above.
        Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this privacy policy? <a href="/contact" class="text-navy-light underline hover:text-navy">Contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
